QuestData.Title: Anima-Laden Dreamcatcher
QuestData.Description: You stumble upon an enchanted dreamcatcher, placed so remotely that it has managed to collect a significant amount of anima without being harvested. Droman Dawnblossom in nearby Dreamsong Fenn would surely appreciate its safe return.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return the Enchanted Dreamcatcher to Droman Dawnblossom in Dreamsong Fenn.
